The paper specifically focuses on the wiretap channel, which is a subfield of cryptography, and therefore, it could also belong to the cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) category. The paper also uses concepts from probability theory and statistics, which suggests that it could belong to the cs.SI (Statistics and Machine Learning) category. The paper provides asymptotic expressions and bounds, which suggests that it could belong to the cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) category. Finally, the paper deals with optimization and tradeoffs, which suggests that it could belong to the cs.LG (Machine Learning) category.
